

Sphinx documentation build procedure:
0. Clean-up
rm -rf docs/sphinx-html/* && rm -rf docs/sphinx/api/*
1. Build HTML documentation
sphinx-build docs/sphinx docs/sphinx-html

Documentation build tools:
1. sphinx with graphviz, autodoc, and viewcode extensions

Test tools:
1. pytest with pep8, html and coverage plugins


Related documentation:
https://learning-0mq-with-pyzmq.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html
https://pyzmq.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
http://zguide.zeromq.org/py:all or http://zguide.zeromq.org/page:all
http://rpymostat.readthedocs.io/en/latest/Discovery.html
